import React from 'react'
import { Fragment } from 'react'
import { Card, Col, Container } from 'react-bootstrap'

const InfoCarrera = () => {
  return (
    <Fragment>
        <Col>
            <Card className="w-75 mb-3">
                <Card.Body></Card.Body>
            </Card>
        </Col>
    </Fragment>
  )
}

export default InfoCarrera
